    "body" : "<p>Ubuntu 20.04,</p>\n<pre><code>GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX=&quot;cgroup_enable=memory swapaccount=1&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p>I had a same issue until I did not <strong>removed</strong> the oom-kill-disable from my yaml file.</p>\n<pre><code>        --memory=1500m \\\n   # --oom-kill-disable \\\n</code></pre>\n"
